{
  "stem": "5103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So if you see anything and you ask it, if you say to that piece of fruit, these apples-- she told me like this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This is in Dutch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She said, if you speak to the apples and you tell them to go away, and they don't go away, then you just take them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You've ask them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They don't go away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So you take them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I-- she used to say, And when he looks the other way, you just pinch and put it on this and run, run for your life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became very smart at this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to say, When are we going out again?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I thought it was a game.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was, you know-- by this time, I was about, I think, about seven and a half, eight.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I started to get very into this, and I quite thought it was good fun, and I was-- for the first time, I was running on the street with her.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what had happened was, this brother-in-law got greedy, and he decided that he's going to do this himself for his family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people, this Anna and her husband, had it into a very good method.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they used to re-arrange the bags back into such a position that nobody would even know there was anything missing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this man went one night, unbeknown to anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had the keys also duplicated, like his brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went and he got coal, and he didn't realize that there's a minute hole in the coal bag.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, when he dragged it at a certain time, whenever they did this, it left a trail from that warehouse, all the way past the house where we were, all the way to his house.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
